1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,202
"Open the locker now." Carter Blake said
it loud enough for everyone in the lobby

2
00:00:05,202 --> 00:00:09,493
to hear. He was thirty-four, sharp
haircut, perfect teeth, MBA from

3
00:00:09,493 --> 00:00:14,500
Vanderbilt — the kind of man who had made
his career by humiliating people who

4
00:00:14,500 --> 00:00:19,636
couldn't fight back, who spoke to farm
