35
00:02:45,115 --> 00:02:46,720
Never explained why.

36
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:53,153
The problem began when the bank got new
ownership. New branding, new computers,

37
00:02:53,153 --> 00:02:58,678
new policies, and a new branch manager
named Carter Blake. Blake was

38
00:02:58,678 --> 00:03:04,781
thirty-four, sharp haircut, perfect
teeth, MBA from Vanderbilt, the kind of

39
00:03:04,781 --> 00:03:11,297
man who could insult you while smiling.
He had been running this branch for four

40
00:03:11,297 --> 00:03:16,080
months when Harold Garrett walked in to
