46
00:03:41,373 --> 00:03:47,228
that means you've spent over two thousand
one hundred dollars protecting what is

47
00:03:47,228 --> 00:03:49,600
almost certainly an empty box.".

48
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:55,172
Harold looked at him. A teller nearby
slowed down just to listen. The lobby

49
00:03:55,172 --> 00:03:56,000
