73
00:05:52,960 --> 00:05:58,347
Blake leaned in, then smiled again. He
picked up the paper, unfolded it. "A

74
00:05:58,347 --> 00:06:03,661
nineteen seventy-one land bond." He
laughed once, the sound echoing in the

75
00:06:03,661 --> 00:06:09,120
cold vault. "A worthless piece of paper.
