80
00:06:29,184 --> 00:06:32,080
today. You may keep your souvenir.".

81
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:37,055
Harold folded the document carefully and
slipped it into his shirt pocket. Then he

82
00:06:37,055 --> 00:06:41,600
