85
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:50,560
Blake thought the old man was confused.
"I'm not clear what you're asking for.".

86
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:55,393
"The federal records. All of them. Every
time the bank acquired property in this

87
00:06:55,393 --> 00:07:00,042
county since nineteen seventy-one. You
filed a review two weeks ago, correct?

88
00:07:00,042 --> 00:07:04,631
That triggered a constructive notice on
every connected property. The county

89
00:07:04,631 --> 00:07:09,280
