111
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:52,076
So Harold paid forty dollars every year.
He did it without fail, without

112
00:08:52,076 --> 00:08:58,065
explanation, without ever opening the
locker. He kept his father's key on his

113
00:08:58,065 --> 00:09:03,897
nightstand, next to the photograph of
George standing in the field with the

114
00:09:03,897 --> 00:09:07,680
hoe. Sometimes he looked at the key and
