193
00:14:46,800 --> 00:14:49,440
Judge Chan turned to Frank Solis.

194
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:52,720
Mr. Solis?

195
00:14:52,720 --> 00:14:57,918
Frank stood. He adjusted his glasses,
looked at the bank's lawyers, and said

196
00:14:57,918 --> 00:15:03,394
