210
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,280
Blake straightened in his chair.

211
00:15:55,280 --> 00:15:59,527
"On the day Mr. Garrett opened his
locker, you laughed at this document in

212
00:15:59,527 --> 00:16:01,680
